name: Expanse
details:
Multi effect pedalIt's a reverb, an echo, a shimmer and a chorus. It's all of these and more! Previously known as our v2 Stereo Pedals, all the pedals in the Expanse Series can be programmed as any effect using Expanse Software:
Reverb (Wet, hall, plate, spring, modulated)
Shimmer
Echo, with/without reverb
Chorus or Detune, with/without reverb
Flanging
Phasing, Phased Doubling
Tremolo
